p freya launched  in the uk by eveden group largebust bras and swimwear up to k cup and sports bras and swimwear up to h cup goddess launched in the usa and acquired in  by eveden group fullfigure bras and swimwear product manufacturingedit wacoal products are manufactured almost entirely by hand using japanese sewing technology as well as continued innovation much of the production occurs at wacoal vietnam a manufacturing location established in  philanthropic effortsedit wacoal launched a bra in  known as the awareness bra which features a pink ribbon on each band to remind women to be conscious of their breast health in  the fit for the cure campaign was launched to raise funds for breast cancer awareness and research wacoal donates to susan g komen for every woman who participates in a complimentary fitting during fit for the cure referencesedit  trademark status  document retrieval tsdrusptogov retrieved  august    human science research center’s activities  wacoal holdings corp wacoal holdings in japanese retrieved  august    the vision of becoming a worldwide company  wacoal holdings corp wacoal holdings in japanese retrieved  august    btemptd btemptd retrieved  august    about us btemptdcouk retrieved  august    our story  wacoal eveden wacoaleuropecom retrieved  august    technique and spirit shared beyond borders wacoal holdings in japanese retrieved  august    wacoal at herroom herroomcom retrieved  august    wacoal  a champion partner for susan g komen® komenorg retrieved  august    herroomcom and wacoal show support for breast cancer awareness marketwiredcom retrieved  august   external linksedit official website wacoal america wacoal europe eveden fantasie freya goddess v t e lingerie upper torso types of bras history bandeau nursing bra sports bra training bra underwire bra male bra other garments babydoll bustier camisole dudou negligee torsolette yếm lower torso bikini boyshorts french knickers girdle girl boxers panties tanga tap pants thong gstri