co ltd and builds interiors for commercial premises the company has operations across japan china france hong kong indonesia malaysia the philippines south korea singapore taiwan thailand the uk the us and vietnam wacoal is headquartered in minamiku kyoto japan the company’s growth strategy envisages maintaining its leadership position in japan and expanding its operations in china the us and europe through acquisitions and strengthening its distribution channels recently the company acquired ukbased eveden group limited a manufacturer and distributor of women’s undergarments and swimming wear with operations across europe americas and asiapacificthis comprehensive swot profile of wacoal holdings corp provides you an indepth strategic swot analysis of the company’s businesses and operations the profile has been compiled by globaldata to bring to you a clear and an unbiased view of the company’s key strengths and weaknesses and the potential opportunities and threats the profile helps you formulate strategies that augment your business by enabling you to understand your partners customers and competitors betterthe profile contains critical company information including business description – a detailed description of the company’s operations and business divisions corporate strategy – analyst’s summarization of the company’s business strategy swot analysis – a detailed analysis of the company’s strengths weakness opportunities and threats company history – progression of key events associated with the company major products and services – a list of major products services and brands of the company key competitors – a list of key competitors to the company key employees – a list of the key executives of the company executive biographies – a brief summary of the executives’ employment history key operational heads – a list of personnel heading key departmentsfunctions important locations and subsidiaries – a list and contact details of key locations and subsidiaries of